---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");
---
<section class="arch">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How it fits together</h2>
    <p class="arch__lead">
      Bridges translate external events into Kubernetes Custom Resources. The run
      platform reconciles them into Jobs. The broker is the only component that
      ever holds long-lived secrets — it gates admission and mints short-lived
      credentials per run.
    </p>
    <svg class="arch__svg" viewBox="0 0 960 360" role="img" aria-labelledby="arch-title">
      <title id="arch-title">Paddock architecture overview</title>

      <!-- External systems -->
      <g class="g-external">
        <rect x="20" y="40" width="160" height="280" rx="8" />
        <text x="100" y="70" text-anchor="middle" class="t-heading">External systems</text>
        <text x="100" y="120" text-anchor="middle">Linear</text>
        <text x="100" y="150" text-anchor="middle">GitHub Issues</text>
        <text x="100" y="180" text-anchor="middle">Slack</text>
        <text x="100" y="210" text-anchor="middle">cron</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Bridges -->
      <g class="g-bridge">
        <rect x="220" y="60" width="180" height="100" rx="8" />
        <text x="310" y="90"  text-anchor="middle" class="t-heading">Bridges</text>
        <text x="310" y="120" text-anchor="middle">webhook → CRD</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Run platform -->
      <g class="g-platform">
        <rect x="440" y="60" width="220" height="100" rx="8" />
        <text x="550" y="90"  text-anchor="middle" class="t-heading">Run platform</text>
        <text x="550" y="120" text-anchor="middle">CRDs · controllers · CLI</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Broker -->
      <g class="g-broker">
        <rect x="700" y="60" width="240" height="100" rx="8" />
        <text x="820" y="90"  text-anchor="middle" class="t-heading">Broker</text>
        <text x="820" y="120" text-anchor="middle">policy · credentials</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Job -->
      <g class="g-job">
        <rect x="220" y="220" width="720" height="120" rx="8" />
        <text x="580" y="248" text-anchor="middle" class="t-heading">Kubernetes Job</text>
        <text x="320" y="278" text-anchor="middle">init: iptables</text>
        <text x="500" y="278" text-anchor="middle">sidecar: proxy</text>
        <text x="680" y="278" text-anchor="middle">sidecar: collector</text>
        <text x="840" y="278" text-anchor="middle">main: agent</text>
        <text x="580" y="312" text-anchor="middle" class="t-muted">workspace PVC · controlled egress</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Arrows -->
      <g class="arrows">
        <line x1="180" y1="110" x2="220" y2="110" />
        <line x1="400" y1="110" x2="440" y2="110" />
        <line x1="660" y1="110" x2="700" y2="110" />
        <line x1="550" y1="160" x2="550" y2="220" />
        <line x1="820" y1="160" x2="820" y2="240" />
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .arch {
    padding-block: var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }
  .arch__lead {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .arch__svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 60rem;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .arch__svg rect {
    fill: var(--color-bg-2);
    stroke: var(--color-rule);
    stroke-width: 1;
  }
  .arch__svg text {
    fill: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .arch__svg .t-heading {
    fill: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .arch__svg .t-muted { fill: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 13px; }
  .arch__svg .arrows line {
    stroke: var(--color-text-muted);
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    marker-end: url(#arrowhead);
  }
  .arch__svg .g-broker rect { stroke: var(--color-accent); stroke-width: 1.5; }
</style>
